These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, pakistani, indonesian, german
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, chess, skydiving, writing
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, september, march, august
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, van, helicopter, ship
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: sunflower, marigold, begonia, aconite
 1. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the pakistani##1
 2. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
 3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person driving the van##1
 4. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
 5. the person driving the airplane is the chinese##1
 6. the person driving the van is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
 7. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the chinese##1
 8. the indonesian is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in march is the chinese##1
10. the person who growsbegonia is the person who's birthday is in september##1
11. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3      |     4      |
| Nationality          | pakistani    | indonesian      | chinese  | german     |
| Hobby         | writing    | skydiving   | card-games | chess      |
| Birthday   | september       | november | march     | august    |
| Transport   | ship | van         | airplane  | helicopter    |
| Flower           | begonia      | aconite       | sunflower | marigold |

