.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-2::.
4 different games are played: snooker, poker, whist, canasta
House: tower, gothic-revival, cape-cod, farmhouse
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, electronic, indie, r&b
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, brazilian, canadian, chinese
There are 4 different favourite colors: blue, pink, white, black
 1. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
 2. the fan of disco is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
 3. the person who likes black is on the right of the chinese##1
 4. the person playing canasta is on the far right##1
 5. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person playing poker##1
 6. the person who likes white is on the right of the person playing whist##1
 7. the fan of r&b is on the right of the tower house##1
 8. the brazilian is the fan of r&b##1
 9. the cape-cod house is the fan of indie##1
10. the fan of disco is on the far right##1
11. the person playing whist is on the left of the japanese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3     |       4       |
| Game      | poker      | snooker     | whist    | canasta |
| House   | tower | gothic-revival   | cape-cod   | farmhouse           |
| Music-Genre   | electronic  | r&b     | indie    | disco         |
| Nationality           | chinese         | brazilian | canadian     | japanese        |
| Color         | blue     | black  | pink | white       |

