.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-3::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, november, may, july
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, salsa, d&b, rock
House: ranch-style, cape-cod, palace, art-deco
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, snowboarding, tennis, weightlifting
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, havana, montecristo, bongani
 1. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in may is the art-deco house##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1
 5. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 6. the bongani-smoker is the person who's birthday is in may##1
 7. the fan of d&b is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
 8. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1
 9. the fan of rock is the cape-cod house##1
10. the fan of salsa is on the left of the palace house##1
11. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the palace house##1
12. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3    |       4       |
| Birthday          | june    | july      | may  | november   |
| Music-Genre   | rock     | d&b      | salsa | house      |
| House           | cape-cod       | ranch-style         | art-deco  | palace         |
| Sport         | basketball | snowboarding | tennis  | weightlifting |
| Cigar     | montecristo       | vegafina         | bongani   | havana        |

