.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, soy-milk, sprite
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, dahlia, daffodil, amaryllis
4 different games are played: canasta, chess, poker, go
There are 4 different favourite colors: lavender, chestnut, amber, blue
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, montecristo, ritmeester, fonseca
 1. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the person who likes lavender##1
 2. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1
 3. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
 4. the person who likes amber is on the far right##1
 5. the havana-smoker is on the far left##1
 6. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
 7. the person playing go is on the far right##1
 8. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the person playing poker##1
 9. the person playing chess is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
10. the person drinking coffee is on the far right##1
11. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left##1
12. the fonseca-smoker is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | soy-milk   | sprite   | cola      | coffee     |
| Flower          | daffodil     | balloon-flower   | amaryllis | dahlia |
| Game   | chess | poker | canasta   | go       |
| Color           | chestnut       | lavender      | blue     | amber |
| Cigar     | havana    | ritmeester     | fonseca     | montecristo     |

