 7. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 8. the person driving the subway is the dancer##1
 9. the person playing backgammon is the person driving the skateboard##1
10. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
11. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
12. the journalist is on the far left##1
13. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
14. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1

.:: Answer ::.
