 9. the architect is on the far right##1
10. the person who likes apricot is the fan of pop##1
11. the person who's hobby is gardening is the person traveling to prague##1
12. the designer is the fan of disco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |      4      |
