.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-17::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, time-travel, martial-arts, mystery
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: rose, iris, poppy, bellflower
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, handball, sailing, climbing
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, dog, hamster, mouse
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, orange, cucumber, artichoke
 1. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 2. the person who growsrose is the person who's sport is skiing##1
 3. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
 4. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1
 5. the person eating artichoke is on the far right##1
 6. the person who growspoppy is on the far left##1
 7. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
 8. the person eating asparagus is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
 9. the person watching epic movies is the person eating orange##1
10. the person watching mystery movies is the owner of the dog##1
11. the person eating cucumber is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
12. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |       2        |      3      |      4       |
| Movie-Genre    | epic     | time-travel  | mystery       | martial-arts      |
| Flower       | poppy    | bellflower        | rose  | iris      |
| Sport         | handball  | climbing | skiing | sailing |
| Pet         | chinchilla | mouse          | dog         | hamster      |
| Food   | orange     | asparagus     | cucumber       | artichoke          |

