.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, mirinda, sprite, water
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, dahlia, balloon-flower, orchid
House: townhouse, farmhouse, victorian, wooden
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, december, july, august
The people have 4 different jobs:  firefighter, fisherman, bartender, mechanic
 1. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far left##1
 2. the person drinking mirinda is the wooden house##1
 3. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the firefighter##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 5. the person who growsballoon-flower is the person drinking sprite##1
 6. the person who growsorchid is the person drinking water##1
 7. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the mechanic##1
 9. the fisherman is the victorian house##1
10. the victorian house is on the far left##1
11. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
12. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the farmhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |      3       |    4     |
| Beverage      | water       | sprite      | mirinda      | juice    |
| Flower         | orchid | balloon-flower | dahlia | bellflower  |
| House   | victorian    | farmhouse     | wooden      | townhouse |
| Birthday   | july  | august     | january    | december  |
| Job           | fisherman  | mechanic       | firefighter          | bartender      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-19::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, prince, pall-mall, alhambra
4 different games are played: snooker, bridge, monopoly, poker
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, horror, mystery, western
The people have 4 different jobs:  writer, project-manager, social-worker, photographer
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, sprite, fanta, hot-chocolate
 1. the social-worker is on the far left##1
 2. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
 3. the person drinking fanta is the person playing monopoly##1
 4. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
 5. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 6. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
 7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the cain-smoker##1
 8. the photographer is on the right of the cain-smoker##1
 9. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the prince-smoker##1
10. the photographer is the pall-mall-smoker##1
11. the writer is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1
12. the person playing bridge is on the far right##1
13. the person playing poker is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |      3      |       4       |
| Cigar          | alhambra      | prince     | cain        | pall-mall     |
| Game         | monopoly     | snooker    | poker | bridge |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | mystery  | horror      | western       |
| Job         | social-worker      | writer | project-manager     | photographer        |
| Beverage     | fanta   | hot-chocolate     | milk  | sprite       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-20::.
There 4 different types of food: apricot, asparagus, cherry, grapes
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: romance, western, musical, documentary
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, skateboarding, weightlifting, snowboarding
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, soul, rock, country
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, aristoff, blend, havana
 1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person watching romance movies##1
 2. the fan of rock is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
 3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
 4. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 5. the fan of rock is the person watching documentary movies##1
 6. the person eating cherry is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
 7. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
 8. the person who's sport is water-polo is the vegafina-smoker##1
 9. the person eating cherry is on the right of the fan of soul##1
10. the person eating grapes is the fan of country##1
11. the fan of country is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
12. the fan of country is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |       3        |      4      |
| Food        | asparagus    | grapes        | apricot        | cherry      |
| Movie-Genre       | musical       | romance       | western      | documentary |
| Sport         | skateboarding | snowboarding | weightlifting | water-polo      |
| Music-Genre         | classical          | country         | soul           | rock    |
| Cigar   | blend         | aristoff       | havana     | vegafina   |

 